{"tid":586540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有茅Ching對KisaBBB條新youtube片好失望","createTime":"2018-03-09T15:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T02:15:17.000Z","uid":65371,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5629a0c50c5af8af33127bb54bdd8a63924eab9e","tid":586540,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:03:50.000Z","msg":"是甘的，Kisa個衰妹呢排見天氣暖左少少就狂po運動bra相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攪到宿宿不行鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/191013_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F191013_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=88add43c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/190350_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F190350_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=62160015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/190400_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F190400_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=24505b20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打左七七四十八次丁之後發現原來BB仲拍埋片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢舖打埋條前列腺出嚟都唔掂牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/190433_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F190433_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff2267f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好喇等我劣左成日鳩keep住個最佳觸感，褲都除埋喇，一開條片，屌你竟然比呢啲我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zd4oG_DzzBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fzd4oG_DzzBY&d=RCy%2F34UwP%2Bv8XPXFD%2BhNpsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=52d93eac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zd4oG_DzzBY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/190411_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F190411_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6d7e4f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">完全吾店牙！<br />\n無線耳筒攞黎做咩架，做運動戴家麻！<br />\n做運動要着咩牙，着運動BRA吖麻！<br />\n做運動要露出KISABBB是常識吧！！！！最少條片都要跳吓彈下，睇下耳筒跌先定個BRA跌先吖嘛吾系甘都唔識拍牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">旺角電腦中心三樓</span></span>平時全層都餵蚊架啦，仆你個街自此以後我搭LIFT永遠只會上二樓牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#本文已置入肥絲推PO參數#"},{"pid":"0d0acd6d7e77a65c38aae5d5072bd654403e05a8","tid":586540,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3b5bf234b3a7510d4662f5b982b1db74cce6c4","tid":586540,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:29:58.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"5f7ed2a0d58bf4a3c8f40d291b503a0cbce37e41","tid":586540,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/10/012550_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F10%2F012550_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9bfc704f&s={